`DHello!` Welcome to my chat script: it makes your text rainbow colored. 

To change `Vchannels` use `Caargon``2.rainbow`{`Nmsg:``V""`, `Nchannel:``V"[new channel]"`} 
To send messages to the cur channel (default `Vtown`), use `Caargon``2.rainbow`{Nmsg:``V"[msg]"`}

I recommend the following macros:
/rc = `Caargon``2.rainbow`{{ Nmsg:``V"{$}"` }}
/cc = `Caargon``2.rainbow`{{ `Nmsg:``V""`, `Nchannel:``V"{0}"` }}
